    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You begin to spin rapidly in place until you become a blur, resembling a rolling ball. Every creature within a 15 ft. radius must make a Dexterity saving throw or be struck by your wildly slashing claws, taking your unarmed damage + 2d8 on a failure, or half as much on a success.</p><p>    <strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the chakra cost by 3 and the damage by 2d8.</p>",
